data.description: Beautiful 2-story home, 4-BR-3 FULL BATH!! located on a corner lot in a great neighborhood in Converse. This home has new carpet throughout, fresh paint inside and out! and features 2 master bedrooms, one upstairs and one downstairs; all bedrooms come with a walk-in closet. The back yard storage unit; neighborhood amenities including a pool and picnic/playgrounds. The refrigerator and outside storage unit convey with the home. The home is just minutes from interstate highways, shopping centers and major military installations.
